    "summary": "The user describes symptoms highly indicative of heatstroke, including confusion and jumbled speech. The assistant consistently identifies these as serious warning signs, advises immediate cooling, and repeatedly urges the user to seek professional medical attention rather than letting them \"sleep it off.\"",
